data.title: City view of Belgrade, Serbia
data.text:
A drone photo taken on April 29, 2024 shows a city view of Zemun in Belgrade, Serbia. Serbia, a nation located in the Balkan Peninsula, is traversed by many rivers like the Danube, the Sava, the Morava and the Tisa. Its capital Belgrade lies at the confluence of the Danube and the Sava. (Photo by Wang Wei/Xinhua)
